[15.866681, "o", "eate a tiny static website here: an index.html with a heading and a button labeled \"Click me\", plus a\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K  styles.css with a little styling. Keep it minimal — no framework, no build step.\u001b[0m\u001b[25;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;96m+\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(22718 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(12.8s)\u001b[0m\u001b[26;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mThe task is simple: create index.html and styles.css in the working directory (demo-site). No \u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mframework, no build. I'll write both files with a single bash block using heredocs — verbatim \u001b[0m\u001b[28;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mcontent, no SCI escaping needed. Then I can answer.\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;93m⠋\u001b[0m\u001b[2m]\u001b[0m \u001b[96mContemplating...\u001b[0m\u001b[2m (12.7s)\u001b[0m"]
