[26.216221, "o", "   • Soft shadow and rounded corners                                                                      \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                          \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mPreview it\u001b[0m                                                                                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[36mopen index.html        # or: python3 -m http.server\u001b[0m                                                      \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                          \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m Open directly in a browser — no dependencies to install. Want me to add a tiny JS click handler or tweak \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m the colors?                                                                                              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m└─────────"]
