[234.29363, "o", "\u001b[1;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2masync mode (default sync false) so it keeps running. I'll launch it and capture the task id.\u001b[0m\u001b[2;1H\u001b[2K  \u001b[36m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mtask$run\u001b[0m({\"job-type\" \"bash\", \"command\" \"python3 -m http.server 800...): called \u001b[2m→\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 8ms, 74 chars\u001b[3;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[1;93m●\u001b[0m \u001b[1mtask-1\u001b[0m - \u001b[2mbash\u001b[0m\u001b[2m · \u001b[0m\u001b[2m0 lines\u001b[0m  \u001b[93mrunning\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(3m)\u001b[0m\u001b[4;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 2 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(23464 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(9.4s)\u001b[0m\u001b[5;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mThe background task was already launched in iteration 1 via task$run (bash, async). It returned \u001b[0m\u001b[6;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mtask-id `task-1` with status `running`, serving the current `demo-site` folder via `python3 -m \u001b[0m\u001b[7;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mhttp.server 8000`. I have everything needed to answer.\u001b[0m\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[9;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────"]
[234.293654, "o", "────────────────────────────────────┐\u001b[0m\u001b[10;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mServer running ✅\u001b[0m                                                                          \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[11;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                            \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[12;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m The \u001b[36mdemo-site/\u001b[0m folder is now being served as a background task.                            \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                            \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mItem\u001b[0m   \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mValue\u001b[0m                                                                            \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m────────┼────────────────────────────\u001b[0m                                                      \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K\u001b["]
