[293.445243, "o", "\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;96m+\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(24909 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(36.6s)\u001b[0m\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mThe task is a simple find/replace in index.html. The `update-file` tool does exactly this and \u001b[0m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mreturns a unified diff. The button text is \"Click me\" → \"Click Me!\". Literal first-match replacement \u001b[0m\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mis fine.\u001b[0m\u001b[25;1H\u001b[2K  \u001b[36m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mupdate-file\u001b[0m({\"path\" \"index.html\", \"pattern\" \">Click me<\", \"replacemen...): called \u001b[2m→\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 30.5s, 340 chars\u001b[31;3H"]
